HEADWORD: Affreightment
<hw>Af*freight"ment</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>affr⟦eacute⟧tement</ets>.]</ety> <def>The act of hiring, or the
